title: Minnesota officer charged with murder in Australian's death: authorities
text:
Minnesota officer charged with murder in Australian's death: authorities Tuesday, March 20, 2018 - 00:44 
The Minneapolis police officer, Mohamed Noor, who fatally shot an unarmed Australian woman last July was arrested on Tuesday on charges of third-degree murder and second-degree manslaughter, prosecutors said. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
